      • Item

        public Item(java.lang.String type,
            double len,
            double wid)
        This constructor receives the item type and its length and width. Invalid values will be set to a default size (9 inches and 10 inches respectively)
        Parameters:
        type - The type of the item (format: String)
        len - The length of the item (format: double)
        wid - The width of the item (format: double)

      • Item

        public Item(java.lang.String type,
            double len,
            double wid,
            double hgt,
            double wgt)
        This constructor receives the item type, its length, width, height, and weight. Invalid values will be set to a default size (9 inches, 10 inches, 1 inch, and 3 kg respectively)
        Parameters:
        type - The type of the item (format: String)
        len - The length of the item (format: double)
        wid - The width of the item (format: double)
        hgt - The height of the item (format: double)
        wgt - The weight of the item (format: double)
